extendedInfo.description: JunglePop is a matching game similar to Bejeweled and Jewels--with a jungle twist! Swap the animals to produce a series of pops, and use fruit bombs to pop multiple animals simultaneously. With smooth gameplay, great graphics, and amazing sounds, JunglePop offers children and adults endless hours of popping fun! Features include:* Standard, Timed, and Infinite game modes* Online leaderboards, local scores and statistics* Save and continue your games effortlessly* Tablet-optimized for a full-screen experience* SD-card enabledJunglePop Free is ad-supported software and works on any Android device running 1.5 or later.  The ad-free version of JunglePop is available for $1.99.
